    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Military bases for the storage and deployment of guided missiles, which are self-propelled projectiles used as weapons, including but not limited to long-range ballistic missiles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
